# Component Creation

## File Structure
When creating a component, ALWAYS generate these 3 files:
1. `ComponentName.tsx` (implementation)
2. `ComponentName.test.tsx` (tests)
3. `ComponentName.stories.tsx` (visual documentation)

## Design Requirements

### Colors
- Background: `#EEEDED`
- Foreground: `#262626`
- Use opacity for variants: `#262626` at 10%, 40%, 60%
- NO other colors (keep it simple)

### Shapes
- Use `<Squircle>` for all rounded elements
- `cornerSmoothing={0.6}` (Dark standard)
